{"tid":1816312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔設小組跟進警暴","createTime":"2020-01-08T07:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T08:30:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb80cfe79ac56ed55b0a289a2f344a44b681316","tid":1816312,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200108/2FOOFLREAND3I4SNHYZBCBFBOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200108%2F2FOOFLREAND3I4SNHYZBCBFBOE%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=0d90c90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200108%2F2FOOFLREAND3I4SNHYZBCBFBOE%2F&h=5391a600\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200108/2FOOFLREAND3I4SNHYZBCBFBOE/</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔設小組跟進警暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200108/large/1578413790_b674.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200108%2Flarge%2F1578413790_b674.gif&h=20432a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新同盟關永業<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今屆大埔區議會屬「全黃」議會，19個民選議席全為民主派人士，昨舉行首次會議由新同盟關永業和獨立泛民劉勇威在無競爭下當選正副主席。關當選主席後發表感言，感謝選民投票對抗極權，承諾未來以公正持平態度做好工作，為30萬大埔區居民求福祉。<br />\n<br />\n區政聯盟區鎮樺代表民主派提出多項會議常規改革，建議由五個委員會增至七個，包括增加政制及保安事務委員會，監察警方及保安局轄下部門行動，同時決議通過設四個直屬大會工作小組，包括跟進反送中運動大埔區內警察暴制工作小組。周炫煒指過去半年警方屢次出現執法問題，期望警方可派分區指揮官出席會議，接受議員質詢，又要求警務處處長鄧炳強出席區議會與議員交流，同時亦決定召開特別大會討論五大訴求、設獨立調查委員會查警暴等。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"ce44fbee06b886f26910d638620366fb64c6670d","tid":1816312,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268a3576221e3d4437ef6e747ac1340d54c0ec2e","tid":1816312,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"Up"},